{"tid":910590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蝗 Effect！東涌超市巨鼠橫行 估計因多了內地人周圍開餐致衞生差","createTime":"2018-11-21T09:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T05:43:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d91fe97fcf77d48be0789c98484de0b06af8a213","tid":910590,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/photo/bkn-20181121160716447-1121_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181121171810\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181121160716447-1121_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181121171810&h=b2fe13ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣涼了，米奇要到超市覓食儲定糧過冬！有讀者昨晚(20日)於東涌東薈城TASTE超級市場外目擊老鼠橫行，米奇更不時東張西望，似乎密謀搵食「開大餐」。讀者陳小姐直言覺得非常惡心，稱以前從未見過老鼠在商場出沒，懷疑因港珠澳大橋開通後令東涌人流急劇增加，以致衞生環境變差，危害居民健康。<br />\n<br />\n「真係覺得好詫異，好惡心！」陳小姐表示，昨晚約11時於東薈城地下搭乘扶手電梯上一樓期間，驚覺樓下B1層有不知名物體在移動，定過神來才發現是一隻大老鼠於TASTE門外的枱櫈亂竄，陳立刻將事件告知商場管理員。<br />\n<br />\n陳續指，TASTE現正進行大裝修，亦增設了不少熟食檔，估計因應大橋通車，<span style=\"color: red;\">多了內地人到TASTE買熟食後，於商場或附近噴水泉空地開餐，令衞生環境變差</span>，擔憂長此下去會造成鼠患，傳播細菌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121160716447-1121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fbkn-20181121160716447-1121_00822_001.html&d=RX7ZHns07AflqApY6FlLgS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=41bf04e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121160716447-1121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d331b2e204af7f1ed10ee7a147697e1ed8cafabb","tid":910590,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9